<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN" "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd"> <html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"> <head> <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" /> <title>i am working as a major incident manager in icici bank project and having 5 years of in major incident manager. </title> </head> <body> <div style="width: 700px;margin: 0 auto;padding:30px 45px;font-family:'Calibri';color:#7F7F7F;background-color:white"> <div style="width:100%;margin-bottom:25px;padding-bottom: 5px;"> <div> <div style="font-size:1.4em;margin-bottom:3px;font-weight:bold;">Durga Prasad</div> <div>  Major Incident Manager at IDC Technologies-Wipro  </div> <div style="font-weight:bold;">    5 Year(s) 0 Month(s) | Hyderabad/Secunderabad | INR 8.20 Lac(s)    </div> </div> <div style="text-align:right">  <div>9505807780</div>   <div>vallamsettydurgaprasad@gmail.com</div>  </div> <div style="width:100%; height:1px; background-color: #d6d6d6; margin-top: 5px"> </div> </div>  <div style="margin-bottom:30px;"> <span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:1.4em;">“</span> i am working as a major incident manager in icici bank project and having 5 years of in major incident manager.  </div>  <div style="margin-bottom:30px;"> <div style="font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:10px;color:#F79647;">WORK SUMMARY</div> <div style="margin-bottom:15px;"> I am working as a major incident manager in ICICI bank project-wipro. I have 5 years of experience in major incident manager.  </div> <div>  <div style="clear: both;display: table;"> <label style="font-weight:bold;vertical-align:top;display:inline-block;margin-bottom:3px;" ><b>Industry : </b></label> <span style="display:inline-block;width:500px">IT Services &amp; Consulting</span> </div>   <div style="clear: both;display: table;"> <label style="font-weight:bold;vertical-align:top;display:inline-block;margin-bottom:3px;"><b>Functional Area : </b></label> <span style="display:inline-block;width:500px">IT &amp; Information Security</span> </div>   <div> <label style="font-weight:bold;vertical-align:top;display:inline-block;margin-bottom:3px;"><b>Role : </b></label> <span style="display:inline-block;width:500px">Incident Management</span> </div>  </div> </div> <div style="margin-bottom:30px;">  <div style="font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:10px;color:#F79647;">WORK EXPERIENCE</div>  <div style="margin-bottom:15px;"> <div style="margin-bottom:3px;">  <span style="font-weight:bold;">Major Incident Manager</span>   <span style="color:#A6A6A5;">Sep 2021 - Till Date</span>  </div>  <div style="color:#4E81BD;font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:3px;">IDC Technologies-Wipro</div>   <div> I have an experience of 5 years in major incident manager.  </div>  </div>  <div style="margin-bottom:15px;"> <div style="margin-bottom:3px;">  <span style="font-weight:bold;">Incident Manager</span>   <span style="color:#A6A6A5;">Sep 2021 - Sep 2021</span>  </div>  <div style="color:#4E81BD;font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:3px;">IDC Technologies</div>   <div> More than 4+ years of Experience in Incident Management, Problem Management, Change Management in various domains (Telecom, Manifacture).Having good exposure in handling Major Incident Management.
Lead problem investigations and find out the root cause of major problems  application outages, major functionalities.
Having experience in implementing Incident, Problem and Change Management process. </div>  </div>   </div> <div style="margin-bottom:30px;">  <div style="font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:10px;color:#F79647;">PROJECT DETAILS</div>  <div style="margin-bottom: 20px;"> <div style="margin-bottom:15px;">  <div style="color:#4E81BD;font-weight:bold;">incident manager</div>   <div style="color:#A6A6A5;">Sep 2021 to Jan 2022</div>  </div> <div style="margin-bottom:15px;">  <div style="clear: both;display: table;"> <label style="font-weight:bold;vertical-align:top;display:inline-block;margin-bottom:3px;margin-right:15px;"><b>Client : </b></label> <span style="display:inline-block;width:500px">Wipro</span> </div>   <div style="clear: both;display: table;"> <label style="font-weight:bold;vertical-align:top;display:inline-block;margin-bottom:3px;margin-right:15px;"><b>Role : </b></label> <span style="display:inline-block;width:500px">99</span> </div>   <div style="clear: both;display: table;"> <label style="font-weight:bold;vertical-align:top;display:inline-block;margin-bottom:3px;margin-right:15px;"><b>Nature of Employment : </b></label> <span style="display:inline-block;width:500px">Full Time</span> </div>   <div style="clear: both;display: table;"> <label style="font-weight:bold;vertical-align:top;display:inline-block;margin-bottom:3px;margin-right:15px;"><b>Role Description : </b></label> <span style="display:inline-block;width:500px">I am an incident manager. I should handle the issues with the help of respective teams to resolve the issue. </span> </div>   <div style="clear: both;display: table;"> <label style="font-weight:bold;vertical-align:top;display:inline-block;margin-bottom:3px;margin-right:15px;"><b>Team Size : </b></label> <span style="display:inline-block;width:500px">12</span> </div>   <div style="clear: both;display: table;"> <label style="font-weight:bold;vertical-align:top;display:inline-block;margin-bottom:3px;margin-right:10px;"><b>Skill Used : </b></label> <span style="display:inline-block;width:500px">ITIL Framework, ITIL, ITIL Certified</span> </div>  </div>  <div> <div style="font-weight:bold;">Project Details:</div> <div> I am working in ITCOMMANDCENTER as a incident manager.  </div> </div>  </div>   </div> <div style="margin-bottom:30px;">  <div style="font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:10px;color:#F79647;">EDUCATION DETAILS</div>  <div style="margin-bottom:15px;"> <div>U.G.</div> <div>B.Tech/B.E. (Mechanical) 2017</div> <div>Raghu Institute of Technology, Visakhapatnam</div> </div>  </div> <div style="margin-bottom:30px;">   </div>  <div style="margin-bottom:30px;"> <div style="font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:10px;color:#F79647;">IT SKILLS</div> <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%" style="border-collapse: collapse;color:#7F7F7F;"> <tr> <th style="text-align:left;padding:8px;background-color:#F6F6F6;border:1px solid #7F7F7F;">Skill Name</th> <th style="text-align:left;padding:8px;background-color:#F6F6F6;border:1px solid #7F7F7F;">Version</th> <th style="text-align:left;padding:8px;background-color:#F6F6F6;border:1px solid #7F7F7F;">Last Used</th> <th style="text-align:left;padding:8px;background-color:#F6F6F6;border:1px solid #7F7F7F;">Experience</th> </tr>  <tr> <td style="padding:8px;border:1px solid #7F7F7F;">MS Office, sql, itil</td> <td style="padding:8px;border:1px solid #7F7F7F;">v3</td> <td style="padding:8px;border:1px solid #7F7F7F;">2020</td> <td style="padding:8px;border:1px solid #7F7F7F;"></td> </tr>  </table> </div>      <div style="margin-bottom:30px;"> <div style="font-weight:bold;top:30px;color:#F79647;">DESIRED JOB DETAILS</div> <div style="clear: both;display: table;">  <label style="font-weight:bold;vertical-align:top;display:inline-block;margin-bottom:3px;width:180px;display:inline-block;"><b>Job Type : </b></label> <span style="display:inline-block;width:500px">Permanent</span>  </div> <div style="clear: both;display: table;">  <label style="font-weight:bold;vertical-align:top;dis